      "content": "wait r u sure? i was worried it might be an infection because of the warmth and the yellow stuff. if it's just normal healing, i don't really want to bother the surgeon since they're probably busy. how long should i keep doing the saltwater soak and ointment before i'd actually need to worry about seeing them?",
